    <item>
      <title>伊姆兰·汗入狱后，谁将成为巴基斯坦的下一任领导人？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/imran-khan-is-in-jail-who-will-become-pakistan-s-next-prime-minister</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦军队长期以来对政治和经济发挥着影响力，没有任何民选领导人能够成功挑战。伊姆兰·汗 (Imran Khan) 在与将军发生争执并在不信任投票中落败后，于 2022 年被罢免总理职务。他于 2023 年因腐败指控入狱，无法参加 2 月 8 日的大选，而军队领导层似乎支持另一位前总理纳瓦兹·谢里夫接替他。但前板球明星汗仍然是最受欢迎的]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/imran-khan-is-in-jail-who-will-become-pakistan-s-next-prime-minister</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 09:59:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>缅甸军方将紧急状态规定再延长六个月</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/myanmar-military-extends-emergency-rule-for-another-six-months</link>
      <description><![CDATA[缅甸军政府周三将紧急状态再延长六个月至 7 月 31 日，陆军参谋长敏昂莱 (Min Aung Hlaing) 担任政变领导人已进入第四个年头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/myanmar-military-extends-emergency-rule-for-another-six-months</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 09:49:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
